Discharge Report for USGS Gauging Station:
Tobacco River near Eureka MT

2021-11-28

This report provides numerous flow statistics at the USGS gauging station Tobacco River near Eureka MT. This is accomplished by generating station statistics through opensource platforms like USGS {DataRetrieval} package (De Cicco et al., 2015) and R (Team, R, 2020). The idea is to give a brief summary of the station (summary stats) and then the user can look through other tabs (hydrograph, bfi, fdc, flood frequency) for deeper analysis.
